{
  "texts": [
    "Simultaneously, the detector employs the encoder's output to classify events as either fake or not.",
    "These three modules are jointly trained to enhance the model's effectiveness.",
    "Huang et al. (2019) proposed a hybrid model for detecting rumors on social media by considering three aspects: users, content and propagation graph.",
    "The model consists of three modules: user encoder, propagation tree encoder and integrator.",
    "The user encoder utilizes GCN to capture and model users' attributes and behaviors."
  ]
}